{"tid":35051,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（支那）研發「合成牛扒」膠漿混碎肉口感嫩口","createTime":"2016-12-11T23:07:28.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-13T04:32:11.000Z","uid":29314,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b489111626204c342a8f240a549cdc6f99ccb04b","tid":35051,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T23:07:28.000Z","msg":"澳洲電視台早前報道，<br />\n<br />\n杭州市面出售大量用黏肉膠做成的合成牛扒，都是用次級牛肉及肉膠製成。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n內地記者近日在浙江杭州採訪發現，市面有多種用以拼接牛排的黏肉膠，有商店出售名為「TG酶」（谷氨酰胺轉氨酶）的食品添加劑，可令碎肉黏合一起，包括牛肉、豬肉，甚至非肉類的植物蛋白也能和肉類黏合。<br />\n<br />\n除了TG酶，杭州調味品市場有店主指，將黃原膠、卡拉膠用在牛扒上，可以在煎牛排的時候鎖住水份，卡拉膠每斤35元人民幣。這些添加劑用法簡單，只要將添加劑加入肉碎中，再用保鮮紙捲起壓實，冰凍後切片，就能做出一片片賣相極佳的合成牛扒。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n內地記者從市面買來肉碎和TG酶，成功製成合成牛扒，將它煎熟後肉質嫩口。"},{"pid":"3c744673c5ff6b4569e5b02f58ae5f63e90d956e","tid":35051,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T23:08:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20161212/large/a1303a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20161212%2Flarge%2Fa1303a.gif&h=97f6935d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fdb8a2323c32b94bea6fd8202d72c28d69bfed7c","tid":35051,"uid":3500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T23:11:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b701f04846a2bb81487c1249583b1a0af031b5c","tid":35051,"uid":4285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T23:13:07.000Z","msg":"用肉頭肉尾痴番埋做扒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bc2e8f50baa3c14300309c301c828a75c6f467a","tid":35051,"uid":7943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T23:14:09.000Z","msg":"千年碎肉變高質牛扒<br />\n大陸真係痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebf25a8ff4e52b78cbb00